    Overview

    Sales automation for LinkedIn. Lead scraping, prospecting & client acquisition for business growth.

    LinkedIn Email Finder & Phone Number Finder Contact Enrichment & LinkedIn Automation Tool Discover verified emails and phone numbers directly on LinkedIn profiles. This powerful tool helps you automate lead generation, export enriched profiles, and personalize outreachall without leaving LinkedIn. Key Features Email & Phone Finder for LinkedIn Access verified contact info using trusted sources like Apollo, FullContact, Hunter.io, Prospeo, and Clay. AI-Powered LinkedIn Automation Send bulk personalized messages, automate connections, and auto-react to postsright inside LinkedIn and Sales Navigator. Auto-Comment with AI on Latest Posts Engage leads with dynamic, intelligent comments on their recent activity. Great for visibility & outreach warm-up. Export Contacts to CSV/CRM Download enriched profiles (name, title, company, contact info) to use in your CRM or outreach tools. Smart Personalization Use dynamic tags like {FirstName}, {Company}, {JobTitle} to personalize every connection and message. Search-Based Lead Extraction Collect leads directly from LinkedIn Search by: Job Title Company Location Industry Language Past Role School & more Sales Navigator Integration Unlock more filters and deeper contact data directly in your workflow. 1-Click Action Buttons Find Email and Find Phone appear directly on profile pagesno switching tools. Included Tools LinkedIn Contact Finder Sales Navigator Lead Extractor Bulk Outreach Message Sender LinkedIn Post Reaction Tool Email & Phone Data Enrichment Engine CSV Import & Export for CRM Integration Perfect For Sales teams building B2B pipelines Recruiters sourcing top talent Founders & marketers doing targeted outreach Growth hackers automating prospecting at scale Why Users Love It 1-click verified contacts Bulk messaging + personalized campaigns Full automation, right inside LinkedIn Clean CSV exports for CRM or email tools No switching apps everything works inside LinkedIn Bonus Tool Also try our AI add-on for Google Sheets: GPT, Perplexity, Mistral, Gemini for programmatic SEO, data enrichment, content generation, and MVP building: https://docgpt.ai/gpt-for-sheets/
